{"tid":2011143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter 手足請多多使用 #香港 hastag","createTime":"2020-05-10T20:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T16:12:35.000Z","uid":200663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4d138958ee7618bcf007a5e05e31de83589ebd3b","tid":2011143,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:14:37.000Z","msg":"依家一入去 #香港 嘅 hashtag page 就會見到：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwVsAEK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwVsAEK.png&h=a71bb2ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個問題 (對家用網軍洗版) 之前已經講過<br />\n雖然一睇佢哋嘅 like 數同 follower 數就知係 bot<br />\n但係試諗下一個台灣/日本人想知多啲香港<br />\n一入到個 hashtag page 見到全部都係對家文宣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家 (尤其係知名人士) 記住<br />\n喺出有關香港嘅 tweet 時 要加 #香港 落去呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時都要同外國知名人士/政客 宣傳多用 #香港 hashtag<br />\n佢哋一個 tweet 隨時 10K like 足以洗走對家文宣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bddc301a9c15d295b1b358aed604ae56aba695d","tid":2011143,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:14:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母開錯台"},{"pid":"bb6b8bf7014f7400c2e76929d98cebccdb46d39c","tid":2011143,"uid":105522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:24:27.000Z","msg":"推 學到嘢 相信大部分Twitter手足主要用英文tweet 以後落埋中文hashtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce331901473f6dcf0b6dc689cff130731d8fecdd","tid":2011143,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:25:12.000Z","msg":"呢邊又推下先"},{"pid":"3f936c71d4a3da49f8388e048e17f4f062be4ad0","tid":2011143,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:26:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb20ff38fb92365afd978cd880f3a329c9380661","tid":2011143,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb6b8bf7014f7400c2e76